room_title: Escape room "Operation: Casino" by Breakout Games - Evansville in Evansville
review: We went with another couple after work to do the Casino mission. First time doing an escape room and it was a great evening. Got to think and work together to solve the clues. We got done with 2 minutes to go. Would like to do another room soon.

room_title: Escape room "Operation: Casino" by Breakout Games - Evansville in Evansville
review: Did the Casino this evening as part of a yearly, family Christmas outing. What a great time! The staff were friendly. Especially Jessica our game master. The puzzles were challenging and fun too. We would do this again.

room_title: Escape room "Operation: Casino" by Breakout Games - Evansville in Evansville
review: We have completed all 4 rooms at Breakout. Each one was challenging, but fun! Highly recommend this for couples, friends, and families!
